  "type": "buff",
  "name": "STRENGTH RANK GRANT",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Template for rank-granting abilities (e.g. the <strong>HIRAISHIN</strong> bloodline). Duplicate this buff onto the actor, rename it to the granting ability, and set its <strong>Level</strong> to the granted rank.</p><p><strong>Grant Mode</strong> (Details tab):</p><ul><li><em>Temporary Ranks</em> — full benefits, no chakra cost, does <strong>not</strong> stack with other ranks (the highest applies).</li><li><em>Rank Bonus</em> — stacks on top of your active rank (e.g. <strong>Order of Fujin</strong>), capped at Rank 10.</li></ul>",
      "instructions": ""
    },
